OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FP&O Ferries faces backlash 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter firing 800 workers   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A backlash against P&O Ferries is      
OL,6, growing after the firm sacked 800 staff
OL,7, without giving them any notice.        
OL,9,FThe government said it would review its
OL,10,Fcontracts with P&O Ferries after it    
OL,11,Ffired its employees, planning to       
OL,12,Freplace them with cheaper agency staff.
OL,14,FUnions hit out against the dismissal,  
OL,15,Fsaying it marked a "dark day" in the   
OL,16,Fshipping industry.                     
OL,18,FP&O said it was a "tough" decision but 
OL,19,Fit would "not be a viable business"    
OL,20,Fwithout the changes.                   
